videos.headline: Stanley outruns Stanford defense for a 55-yard TD
videos.description: Sam Noyer throws to Dimitri Stanley, who turns on the jets and breaks free for a 55-yard Colorado touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Stanley outruns Stanford defense for a 55-yard TD) 2020/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Colorado QB Noyer lunges his way in for a TD
videos.description: Sam Noyer fakes the handoff and takes it in himself, lunging into the end zone from seven yards out.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Colorado QB Noyer lunges his way in for a TD) 2020/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Noyer runs in his 2nd TD of the game for Colorado
videos.description: Sam Noyer keeps it himself again and runs in a 10-yard touchdown to increase Colorado's lead over Stanford.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Noyer runs in his 2nd TD of the game for Colorado) 2020/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jerry Rice's son makes 34-yard catch for first collegiate TD
videos.description: Brenden Rice, the son of Jerry Rice, runs in 34-yard catch for the first college touchdown of his career vs. Stanford.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jerry Rice's son makes 34-yard catch for first collegiate TD) 2020/11/14 ESHEET
